    <title>"Uncaught TypeError" during "EnrichFinance" Step in "Business Partner Creation Approval Process"</title>
    <updated>2024-06-13T12:42:47.509000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>headofants</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/842187</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;We have imported and testing "Business Partner Creation Approval Process" live process project from SAP Build Process Automation Store.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are able to reach until "EnrichFinance" step without any issues.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="headofants_0-1718274880723.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123097i84082EA8781F4AA1/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="headofants_0-1718274880723.png" alt="headofants_0-1718274880723.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;But on "EnrichFinance" step, when we're trying to add Bank or Tax Data in My Inbox task, nothing happens.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="headofants_1-1718274934383.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123098i8D7656BD868A8D5E/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="headofants_1-1718274934383.png" alt="headofants_1-1718274934383.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;There are no calls being made to any URL.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="headofants_2-1718274970502.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123099iCED86C7577BA822D/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="headofants_2-1718274970502.png" alt="headofants_2-1718274970502.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;But in Console, we see errors when we are clicking on "+" button&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For Bank Data -&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="headofants_3-1718275041481.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123102i9D88B01F0207A8AC/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="headofants_3-1718275041481.png" alt="headofants_3-1718275041481.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For Tax Data -&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="headofants_4-1718275074175.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123103iBCB31C7D94E6A52B/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="headofants_4-1718275074175.png" alt="headofants_4-1718275074175.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Upon navigation to the referenced Component-preload.js, we see below line of code in failed state -&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="headofants_5-1718275145994.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123104iF46B6D45A04C6B67/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="headofants_5-1718275145994.png" alt="headofants_5-1718275145994.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-javascript"&gt;&lt;code&gt;onAddTaxNumber: function() {
                        var e = this.getParentModel().getProperty("/BPRequest/FinanceData/TaxData");
                        e.push({
                            TaxCategory: "",
                            TaxNumber: ""
                        });
                        this.getParentModel().setProperty("/BPRequest/FinanceData/TaxData", e);
                        this.getParentModel().refresh()
                    },&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;Trigger to the process -&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are triggering process via API. Below is our payload -&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-json"&gt;&lt;code&gt;{
  "RequestId": "1718213572",
  "BPRequest": {
    "BusinessPartnerCategory": "2",
    "BusinessPartnerName": "Bhupesh LLC",
    "RolesData": [
      {
        "BusinessPartnerRole": "Z001"
      }
    ],
    "AddressData": {
      "Country": "IN",
      "PostalCode": "400101",
      "CityName": "Mumbai"
    }
  },
  "RequesterDetails": {
    "RequesterUserId": "P000001",
    "RequesterFirstName": "Bhupesh",
    "RequesterLastName": "Yadav",
    "RequesterEmail": "&amp;lt;hidden&amp;gt;"
  },
  "internal": {
    "isRework": false
  }
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;Please let us know if we are missing anything.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/quot-uncaught-typeerror-quot-during-quot-enrichfinance-quot-step-in-quot/qaq-p/13729629"/>
    <published>2024-06-13T12:42:47.509000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
